text: Zane Edward Green was born 11 October, 1996 in Windhoek. He is a cricketer from Namibia who played 8 One-day Internationals and 16 Twenty20 Internationals. He is a wicket-keeper and left-handed batsman. ==Other websites== * * Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Namibian cricketers Category:People from Windhoek
